# Simplicity

Favor simple, straightforward solutions over complex ones, avoiding unnecessary abstractions or over-engineering.

**Justification**: Simplicity reduces technical debt and enhances maintainability.

**Example**: Use basic hooks in `HomeTab.tsx` instead of complex state management unless needed.

**Related Rules**: [separation-of-concerns.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/01-code-standards/separation-of-concerns.mdc), [single-responsibility.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/01-code-standards/single-responsibility.mdc)
